task.summary: adjusted break points and column sizes to achieve line lengths around 50 characters.
A folder can now be assigned a position.
Organized folder locations so they don't stack.
Folders are now created in the #desktop container instead of the of the document body.
Clicking on a folder icon now opens a base folder.
Changed background from solid color to image.
The Folder module can now open and close a base _WindowContainer.
Refactored creation of desktop to new module that reads registry.
Refactored creation of desktop to new module that reads registry.
Fixed issue with _WindowContainer not opening when user clicks a folder.
Changed Dojo from CDN to local build.
recommit after I messed up the repository...
Desktop items are now called through switch statement.
Fixed issue where files attributes was accidently renamed.
added working grid displaying data from a simple JavaScript data source
